---
import DocsLayout from '../../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---
<DocsLayout title="发布与安装" slug="usage/publish-install" lang="zh" description="prime publish / prime install 的闭环 —— Skill tarball、semver、registry。">
  <h1>发布与安装</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--fg-muted);">
    分发只走 HTTP —— 任何实现了
    <a href="/zh/docs/spec/registry">registry 契约</a>的服务都是 registry。
    参考实现就一个文件。
  </p>

  <h2>起一个 registry</h2>
<pre><code>{`# Run the reference registry on port 4000 (SQLite-backed pack store).
bun run packages/registry/src/index.ts --port 4000

# Or use Docker if you prefer:
docker run -p 4000:4000 \\
  -v $(pwd)/registry-data:/data \\
  ghcr.io/skill-wiki/registry:0.1.0`}</code></pre>

  <h2>写一份 Skill manifest</h2>
  <p>在 Skill 根目录放一份 <code>pack.yaml</code>：</p>

<pre><code>{`name: "@my/cooking"
version: "1.0.0"
description: "Cooking knowledge — methods, terms, and rules."
license: Apache-2.0

prime-version: "1.0"
sources: "primes/sources"
compiled: "primes/compiled"`}</code></pre>

  <h2>发布</h2>
<pre><code>{`# Compile first (publish bundles compiled/)
bun scripts/build-atom-dirs.ts \\
  --src primes/sources \\
  --out primes/compiled

# Publish
prime publish --remote http://localhost:4000

# What it does:
# 1. Tarball the pack (excluding node_modules, .git, .l2-cache.json)
# 2. Compute sha256
# 3. POST /publish with manifest + tarball
# 4. Print the assigned URL`}</code></pre>

  <h2>安装</h2>
<pre><code>{`# Install into ./.primes/
prime install @my/cooking --remote http://localhost:4000

# With a version range
prime install '@my/cooking@^1.0' --remote http://localhost:4000

# Install everything declared in SKILL.md frontmatter
prime install --remote http://localhost:4000`}</code></pre>

  <h2>版本</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Skill semver：</strong>patch = 原子内容修改，minor = 新增原子，major = 删原子或删 verb。</li>
    <li><strong>原子 semver：</strong>每个原子内部通过 <code>version: "x.y.z"</code> 字段独立版本。</li>
    <li><strong>解析：</strong>取匹配范围的最新版本；锁文件是 <code>.primes/lock.yaml</code>。</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>验证安装</h2>
<pre><code>{`prime ls --dir .primes
# → @my/cooking @ 1.0.0

prime list --dir .primes/@my/cooking/primes/compiled
# → ... atoms ...`}</code></pre>

  <h2>闭环测试</h2>
  <p>完整闭环在 <code>scripts/test-registry-roundtrip.sh</code>：</p>

<pre><code>{`bash scripts/test-registry-roundtrip.sh
# 1. Boot a clean registry
# 2. Publish examples/recipes
# 3. Install in a fresh dir
# 4. Diff compiled artifacts
# 5. Tear down`}</code></pre>

  <h2>认证</h2>
  <p>
    参考 registry 用 bearer token 鉴权 <code>POST /publish</code>；读操作公开。
    通过 registry CLI 签发 token：
  </p>

<pre><code>{`bun run packages/registry/src/cli.ts token create --org skill-wiki
# → token: pri_token_...

# Use it
prime publish --remote http://localhost:4000 --token pri_token_...`}</code></pre>

  <h2>托管选项</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>自托管：</strong>在任何能跑 Node 的虚机上跑参考 registry，约 50 MB 内存。</li>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare Workers：</strong>参考实现可平滑移植，pack 存储用 R2。</li>
    <li><strong>静态 + CDN：</strong>只读分发，公开的 S3 桶 + 一份 manifest 索引就够。</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
